t certain persons try to tarnish the image of the hospital by spreading false messages and information that are inaccurate.   THE University of Port Harcourt Teaching Hospital, UPTH, has received medical equipment for its new Assisted Reproductive Unit, ARU, designed to enable couples having challenges of infertility give birth to children. In "Health" Aggrieved University of Port Harcourt, UNIPORT, students have chased away all the doctors and nurses at the University of Port Harcourt Traching Hospital and locked up the hospital gate, barring movement in and out of the health facility. In "News" PORT HARCOURT: The University of Port Harcourt Teaching Hospital, UPTH, has commenced testing for COVID-19 in Rivers State. In "News"